      "title": "Lanka IOC distribution continues",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "COLOMBO (News 1st); The Ceylon Petroleum Private Tanker Owners\u2019 Association says that the fuel owned by the Lanka IOC is continuously distributed throughout the country.",
        "Protest, altercations as well as long queues have become a common sight at almost every filling station in the country.",
        "The Joint Secretary of the Ceylon Petroleum Private Tanker Owners\u2019 Association Shanta Silva said that about 100 tankers have been deployed daily for the transportation of Lanka IOC fuel."
      ],
